Maintainer: Andreas Oberritter <obi@saftware.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5)
Standards-Version: 3.8.0
Section: libs

Package: libdvbsi++-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libdvbsi++1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: A free DVB SI parser library written in C++
 With libdvbsi++ you can convert raw DVB service information
 to a set of C++ objects, removing the need to parse data
 manually.

